{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Liquor Store Simulator</strong> is a simulator game about the development of your store. You start your business in a small store that you bought on credit.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At first, it will not be easy \u2014 you will have to work independently at the checkout, accept goods, keep records and keep order in the trading floor. But hard work and smart solutions will help you turn a modest outlet into a thriving store with a wide assortment and satisfied customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase goods and arrange the trading equipment at your discretion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/1.png?t=1735560599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Alcohol licenses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy alcohol licenses. This way you will get access to more expensive and premium drinks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/2.png?t=1735560599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Personnel management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the beginning, you'll have to do everything yourself. But as your store develops, you will no longer be able to cope alone. Hire employees to effectively manage your store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/3.png?t=1735560599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Change the color of the walls, ceiling, and floor. Make your store unique and different from others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama